data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELED for 11/11/23. Home is UCCS. Impeccably kept 4 BD and 4 full bath rancher located close to the Linwood/ Somers Point border. This is a great open floor plan and perfect for entertaining. There is a large family room with a gas fireplace and custom-built ins. This is located off of the kitchen which also has a breakfast room. The dishwasher and refrigerator are new. The pantry is also oversized. The Master BD has its own private en suite with a Jacuzzi tub, a large walk-in custom shower and new glass door recently installed. There is also a large walk-in closet. There are 2 large bedrooms with one having a full bath in the hall and the other having its own private full bath in the BD. The loft, which consists of another large BD and another full bath could be a perfect set up for extended family and or In-law suite. The outside features a beautiful inground pool which includes a security fence, new pool heater, filter, manifold, and motor. There is also irrigation and a white vinyl fenced in yard. The front of the home is beautifully landscaped and also has custom lighting that is on a timer. Improvements include but not limited, new HVAC and Navien Tankless Water Heater. Both sets of French doors have new TREX landings, steps and rails. Seller is including the new security system and Ring doorbell. Since purchasing the home, seller has spent more than $65K in improvements. Please look under Associated Docs for a list of upgrades. The seller also replaced the side roof to accommodate the Solar Panels. This is leased (25 years) $155.08 a month and the buyer will be responsible to take over the lease at closing.
